WEBVTT

1
00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:52.987
Kitana...

2
00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:54.722
I have something for you.

3
00:00:55.455 --> 00:00:57.057
It will protect you.

4
00:00:58.358 --> 00:01:00.327
It's beautiful. Father.

5
00:01:02.129 --> 00:01:04.032
This was a gift
from Lord Raiden.

6
00:01:04.164 --> 00:01:05.567
The God of Thunder.

7
00:01:06.668 --> 00:01:09.102
If anything
were to happen to me.

8
00:01:09.236 --> 00:01:11.305
he's always listening.

9
00:01:18.345 --> 00:01:21.148
Shao Kahn
is arriving. Your Majesty.

10
00:01:21.281 --> 00:01:24.184
What happens if you lose?

11
00:01:24.318 --> 00:01:25.485
Don't worry
about that.

12
00:01:25.620 --> 00:01:27.387
But what if he's too strong?

13
00:01:27.522 --> 00:01:29.991
Strength is not a closed fist.

14
00:01:30.123 --> 00:01:31.425
Strength is here.

15
00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:33.661
and here.

16
00:01:36.798 --> 00:01:38.866
Be strong. Kitana.

17
00:01:45.172 --> 00:01:50.110
Jerrod. our king!
Jerrod. our king!

18
00:02:04.659 --> 00:02:07.629
<i>Shao Kahn.</i>
<i>Emperor of Outworld.</i>

19
00:02:07.762 --> 00:02:11.566
<i>sought to unite the various</i>
<i>realms under one rule.</i>

20
00:02:11.699 --> 00:02:13.801
<i>His.</i>

21
00:02:13.935 --> 00:02:17.605
<i>But the Elder Gods had put</i>
<i>certain precautions in place.</i>

22
00:02:20.041 --> 00:02:23.578
<i>Our fates would not be settled</i>
<i>by the size of our armies.</i>

23
00:02:25.647 --> 00:02:29.316
<i>They would be decided</i>
<i>by combat.</i>

24
00:02:30.484 --> 00:02:32.587
<i>The rules were simple.</i>

25
00:02:32.720 --> 00:02:35.890
<i>If one realm could win</i>
<i>10 tournaments in a row.</i>

26
00:02:36.024 --> 00:02:39.127
<i>it would be given</i>
<i>dominion over the other.</i>

27
00:02:39.259 --> 00:02:43.230
<i>Outworld would be allowed</i>
<i>to pillage Edenia's resources.</i>

28
00:02:44.364 --> 00:02:46.333
<i>Enslave our people.</i>

29
00:02:50.038 --> 00:02:54.676
<i>This was the final tournament.</i>
<i>Our last chance.</i>

30
00:02:54.809 --> 00:02:57.879
<i>All of our greatest warriors</i>
<i>had already fallen.</i>

31
00:02:59.413 --> 00:03:01.683
<i>Only one fighter remained.</i>

32
00:03:01.816 --> 00:03:03.316
<i>My father.</i>

33
00:03:04.519 --> 00:03:07.789
<i>King Jerrod of Edenia.</i>

34
00:03:07.922 --> 00:03:11.224
<i>But he faced Outworld's</i>
<i>greatest warrior.</i>

35
00:03:13.260 --> 00:03:15.697
<i>Shao Kahn himself.</i>

36
00:03:25.740 --> 00:03:29.977
They will never bow to you.

37
00:03:30.111 --> 00:03:32.046
We shall see.

38
00:04:28.368 --> 00:04:29.504
Never!

39
00:05:24.959 --> 00:05:27.261
Kitana.
close your eyes.

40
00:05:27.394 --> 00:05:28.863
Close your eyes right now.

41
00:05:43.144 --> 00:05:46.247
No!

42
00:05:46.379 --> 00:05:47.882
No!

43
00:05:50.251 --> 00:05:53.453
No!

44
00:06:24.018 --> 00:06:27.321
Edenia
now belongs to me.

45
00:07:05.626 --> 00:07:08.729
Kneel.
Or you'll die.

46
00:08:16.030 --> 00:08:18.766
Your father shouldn't have
brought you here.

47
00:08:30.244 --> 00:08:33.247
Kitana.
you're my daughter now.

48
00:08:47.528 --> 00:08:48.529
Kitana!

49
00:09:25.433 --> 00:09:26.300
Yield.

50
00:09:45.953 --> 00:09:48.122
You cannot be serious.

51
00:09:48.255 --> 00:09:51.092
You're the one who taught me.
everything's a weapon.

52
00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:00.968
You yield.

53
00:10:15.349 --> 00:10:16.750
What do you have there?

54
00:10:16.884 --> 00:10:18.385
It's nothing.

55
00:10:19.787 --> 00:10:20.888
Jade.

56
00:10:22.923 --> 00:10:24.358
It was 20 years ago today

57
00:10:24.492 --> 00:10:26.827
the Emperor named me
as your bodyguard.

58
00:10:27.895 --> 00:10:30.197
I know what Shao Kahn
took from you.

59
00:10:30.331 --> 00:10:32.433
And if you had been vicious
or cruel to me.

60
00:10:32.567 --> 00:10:33.734
no one would have blamed you.

61
00:10:33.868 --> 00:10:36.737
but you treated me
like family.

62
00:10:37.705 --> 00:10:38.906
Like a sister.

63
00:10:40.875 --> 00:10:43.043
You are my sister.

64
00:10:43.177 --> 00:10:45.146
In every way that matters.

65
00:10:47.982 --> 00:10:51.952
Um. I got you something.
For the tournament.

66
00:10:56.724 --> 00:10:58.159
I was told
that a proper princess

67
00:10:58.292 --> 00:11:01.428
is supposed to sit around
on pillows fanning herself.

68
00:11:02.763 --> 00:11:04.098
Then I thought

69
00:11:04.231 --> 00:11:07.434
you are not exactly
the pillow type.

70
00:11:11.906 --> 00:11:13.307
These are amazing.

71
00:11:26.487 --> 00:11:28.590
Hello. Mother.

72
00:11:28.722 --> 00:11:32.226
I was beginning
to think you were avoiding me.

73
00:11:32.359 --> 00:11:35.162
I've been busy.
Training for the tournament.

74
00:11:36.797 --> 00:11:38.766
Good.
Because I have petitioned

75
00:11:38.899 --> 00:11:41.368
the Elder Gods
for the tournament to begin.

76
00:11:41.503 --> 00:11:44.673
Let Raiden scrounge
for his little champions.

77
00:11:44.805 --> 00:11:47.441
They will simply
be the first to die

78
00:11:47.576 --> 00:11:49.443
and Earthrealm will be mine.

79
00:11:55.916 --> 00:11:57.218
Why is he here?

80
00:11:57.351 --> 00:11:59.920
I have a task
for Shang Tsung.

81
00:12:00.988 --> 00:12:03.724
I hope you bring
good news. Sorcerer.

82
00:12:03.857 --> 00:12:06.561
My spies have located
the relic.

83
00:12:06.695 --> 00:12:08.395
It was last seen
in Raiden's temple

84
00:12:08.530 --> 00:12:12.032
where it was stolen
by the mercenary. Kano.

85
00:12:12.166 --> 00:12:14.569
We seek the Amulet of Shinnok.

86
00:12:14.703 --> 00:12:17.639
It is said the Amulet
can heal any wound.

87
00:12:17.771 --> 00:12:19.873
Transform a man into a god.

88
00:12:20.007 --> 00:12:21.576
To charge the amulet
would require

89
00:12:21.710 --> 00:12:23.744
an impossible amount of power.

90
00:12:23.877 --> 00:12:26.814
We would need to capture
a star from the heavens.

91
00:12:26.947 --> 00:12:29.584
A star...

92
00:12:29.718 --> 00:12:32.119
...or a god.

93
00:12:32.253 --> 00:12:34.255
Outworld has issued
their challenge

94
00:12:34.388 --> 00:12:36.056
and the Elder Gods
have spoken.

95
00:12:36.190 --> 00:12:40.629
When the sand is gone.
the first round will begin.

96
00:12:40.761 --> 00:12:43.330
Mortal Kombat is upon us

97
00:12:43.464 --> 00:12:47.001
and yet we are still short
one champion.

98
00:13:07.288 --> 00:13:09.691
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

99
00:13:09.823 --> 00:13:15.262
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

100
00:13:41.088 --> 00:13:43.991
It's showtime.

101
00:13:48.697 --> 00:13:50.864
♪ <i>Are you ready. baby?</i> ♪

102
00:13:59.940 --> 00:14:01.241
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

103
00:14:02.544 --> 00:14:05.913
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

104
00:14:07.915 --> 00:14:10.150
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

105
00:14:10.284 --> 00:14:12.419
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

106
00:14:22.564 --> 00:14:24.932
You should have
brought more guys.

107
00:14:25.065 --> 00:14:26.568
♪ <i>The sun comes out</i> ♪

108
00:14:26.701 --> 00:14:30.605
♪ <i>Last night was shaking</i>
<i>And pretty loud</i> ♪

109
00:14:32.507 --> 00:14:34.375
♪ <i>It scratches my skin</i> ♪

110
00:14:34.509 --> 00:14:38.513
♪ <i>So what is wrong</i>
<i>With another sin?</i> ♪

111
00:14:44.485 --> 00:14:46.588
♪ <i>Yeah. yeah. yeah. yeah</i> ♪

112
00:14:46.721 --> 00:14:48.989
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

113
00:14:49.123 --> 00:14:51.760
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

114
00:14:51.892 --> 00:14:54.395
♪ <i>Come on. come on</i>
<i>Come on. come on</i> ♪

115
00:14:56.664 --> 00:14:58.165
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

116
00:14:58.298 --> 00:15:00.234
Man. Johnny Cage
got old as fuck.

117
00:15:06.206 --> 00:15:07.876
<i>Attention. fans.</i>

118
00:15:08.008 --> 00:15:10.010
<i>don't miss your chance to meet</i>
<i>your favorite influencers</i>

119
00:15:10.144 --> 00:15:12.946
<i>and YouTube stars</i>
<i>in Autograph Alley.</i>

120
00:15:13.080 --> 00:15:14.816
All right.
everyone. get in close.

121
00:15:14.948 --> 00:15:15.916
Black Orchid!

122
00:15:25.894 --> 00:15:27.227
<i>It's showtime.</i>

123
00:15:43.043 --> 00:15:44.779
Johnny Cage.

124
00:15:44.913 --> 00:15:47.649
Hey. guys. I'm off the clock.

125
00:15:47.782 --> 00:15:51.853
Mr. Cage. you have been chosen
for Mortal Kombat.

126
00:15:52.019 --> 00:15:53.588
Mortal Kombat. huh?

127
00:15:53.721 --> 00:15:55.690
What's that?
Some kind of fan film?

128
00:15:55.824 --> 00:15:57.257
It's a fighting tournament.

129
00:15:57.391 --> 00:16:00.394
Yeah. not really
my thing anymore.

130
00:16:02.262 --> 00:16:03.765
Unless it's a paying gig?

131
00:16:03.898 --> 00:16:06.568
More like a "fate
of the entire human race" gig.

132
00:16:06.701 --> 00:16:09.571
Tell me you're
not some crazy fans.

133
00:16:09.704 --> 00:16:11.271
Definitely not fans.

134
00:16:11.405 --> 00:16:13.273
All right. All right.
You don't
have to say "definitely."

135
00:16:13.407 --> 00:16:14.642
You have been chosen

136
00:16:14.776 --> 00:16:16.578
as one of the champions
of Earthrealm.

137
00:16:16.711 --> 00:16:20.180
The gods have selected you.
Mr. Cage.

138
00:16:20.314 --> 00:16:22.650
All right. I think it's time
for you guys to fuck off.

139
00:16:22.784 --> 00:16:25.219
But. hey. love the cosplay.
What's that?

140
00:16:25.352 --> 00:16:27.254
<i>Big Trouble in Little China?</i>
Fantastic film.

141
00:16:27.387 --> 00:16:28.957
Listen. I know
what it sounds like.

142
00:16:29.089 --> 00:16:30.457
but he's telling the truth.

143
00:16:30.592 --> 00:16:33.795
Very soon the champions
will be summoned to fight

144
00:16:33.928 --> 00:16:35.195
and you will be among them.

145
00:16:35.329 --> 00:16:36.631
The fate of your world

146
00:16:36.764 --> 00:16:39.266
rests on the outcome
of this tournament.

147
00:16:39.399 --> 00:16:41.936
Fantastic.
I will see you there.

148
00:16:42.069 --> 00:16:43.538
Thanks for coming. drive safe.

149
00:16:43.671 --> 00:16:45.940
and. uh. say hi to Dumbledore
for me.

150
00:16:46.073 --> 00:16:48.075
You're gonna have to show him.

151
00:17:02.256 --> 00:17:04.659
Holy shit.

152
00:17:04.792 --> 00:17:06.093
How are you doing that?

153
00:17:06.226 --> 00:17:07.729
Come with us.
Mr. Cage.

154
00:17:07.862 --> 00:17:10.798
and discover the man
you were meant to be.

155
00:17:17.271 --> 00:17:19.072
Now are you coming or what?

156
00:17:44.398 --> 00:17:47.200
Where the hell am I?

157
00:17:47.334 --> 00:17:49.236
It's okay.
You're still on Earth.

158
00:17:49.369 --> 00:17:51.104
Welcome
to Raiden's Sky Temple.

159
00:17:57.612 --> 00:18:00.548
Watch this.

160
00:18:00.682 --> 00:18:04.719
Robot arms.
That dude's got robot arms.

161
00:18:04.852 --> 00:18:06.320
We served
in the Army together.

162
00:18:06.453 --> 00:18:08.756
That's Jax Briggs.
Special Forces.

163
00:18:09.991 --> 00:18:11.325
That's Cole Young.

164
00:18:11.458 --> 00:18:14.361
His suit absorbs attacks
and makes him stronger.

165
00:18:14.494 --> 00:18:15.830
He's a descendant of Scorpion.

166
00:18:15.964 --> 00:18:18.365
One of Earthrealm's
greatest warriors.

167
00:18:19.232 --> 00:18:20.167
Oh.

168
00:18:20.300 --> 00:18:22.135
That's Liu Kang.

169
00:18:22.269 --> 00:18:24.171
He's the best fighter we got.

170
00:18:32.680 --> 00:18:34.849
- He shoots fire?
- Mm-hmm.

171
00:18:36.718 --> 00:18:40.088
I feel like that's cheating.
but okay.

172
00:18:40.220 --> 00:18:41.388
It kind of feels like bullshit

173
00:18:41.522 --> 00:18:43.223
that y'all have
these crazy powers

174
00:18:43.357 --> 00:18:46.527
and I'm just. you know.
incredibly handsome.

175
00:18:46.661 --> 00:18:48.062
It could take
months of training

176
00:18:48.195 --> 00:18:49.731
to unlock your powers.

177
00:18:49.864 --> 00:18:51.198
We don't have
that kind of time.

178
00:18:51.331 --> 00:18:52.567
Yeah.
well. whose fault is that?

179
00:18:52.700 --> 00:18:54.301
I mean.
if you knew this was coming.

180
00:18:54.434 --> 00:18:55.770
why'd you wait till the
last second to find me?

181
00:18:55.903 --> 00:18:58.506
We used to have
another champion. Kung Lao.

182
00:18:58.640 --> 00:19:00.240
Oh. great.
so I'm just the fucking sub.

183
00:19:00.374 --> 00:19:02.376
He was murdered.
By Shang Tsung.

184
00:19:02.510 --> 00:19:04.846
Wait. Murdered?

185
00:19:06.446 --> 00:19:08.816
Come on.
You can't be serious. Right?

186
00:19:08.950 --> 00:19:11.719
I mean. that's. like.
gotta be against the rules.

187
00:19:11.853 --> 00:19:14.254
You can't just go around
killing people.

188
00:19:15.455 --> 00:19:18.793
It's called Mortal Kombat
for a reason.

189
00:19:18.926 --> 00:19:22.130
Yo. Gandalf. send me back.
I wanna go back.

190
00:19:22.262 --> 00:19:24.599
-Johnny. wait.
-No. No.

191
00:19:24.732 --> 00:19:26.534
You said tournament
which implies rules.

192
00:19:26.668 --> 00:19:28.603
and a referee. and I don't
know. maybe a medic.

193
00:19:28.736 --> 00:19:30.772
Not some fucking <i>Squid Game</i>
murder party.

194
00:19:30.905 --> 00:19:33.041
Dude wants to quit.
just let him go.

195
00:19:33.173 --> 00:19:34.509
We don't need him.

196
00:19:34.642 --> 00:19:37.277
Look. you wanna step
in the octagon

197
00:19:37.411 --> 00:19:38.780
with a bunch
of happy assholes

198
00:19:38.913 --> 00:19:42.016
that don't know how to lose.
go right ahead.

199
00:19:42.150 --> 00:19:44.351
But I don't have
Transformer arms.

200
00:19:44.484 --> 00:19:47.387
or shoot lightning bolts
or fireballs.

201
00:19:47.522 --> 00:19:49.857
or do whatever the fuck it is
Flame Fingers does.

202
00:19:49.991 --> 00:19:53.326
so forgive me if I don't
sign up to get mulched.

203
00:19:56.698 --> 00:19:59.266
You are not wrong. Mr. Cage.

204
00:20:07.240 --> 00:20:08.976
Nine times.
we have been challenged.

205
00:20:09.110 --> 00:20:10.878
And nine times. we have lost.

206
00:20:11.012 --> 00:20:12.580
And now. 20 years later.

207
00:20:12.714 --> 00:20:16.684
Shao Kahn seeks to add
Earthrealm to his dominion.

208
00:20:16.818 --> 00:20:20.688
This is a war
for the fate of your world.

209
00:20:20.822 --> 00:20:23.725
Look. Cage. I get it.
We all do.

210
00:20:23.858 --> 00:20:25.660
Some stupid. fucking.
cosmic lottery

211
00:20:25.793 --> 00:20:28.963
decided that we're the ones
that get to save the world.

212
00:20:31.331 --> 00:20:33.201
Shit is terrifying.

213
00:20:33.333 --> 00:20:35.435
You wanna know
the last thing I did
before coming here?

214
00:20:35.570 --> 00:20:38.840
I said goodbye to my wife
and my little girl.

215
00:20:38.973 --> 00:20:42.275
The two most important things
in my life.

216
00:20:42.409 --> 00:20:43.477
And there's a damn good chance

217
00:20:43.611 --> 00:20:45.680
I'm never
gonna see them again.

218
00:20:47.148 --> 00:20:49.117
And I'm okay with that.

219
00:20:49.249 --> 00:20:52.587
Because I know if I die
out there. I'm dying for them.

220
00:20:53.755 --> 00:20:56.224
We lose one more time.
the Earth is gone.

221
00:20:56.356 --> 00:20:59.459
And our only chance
is to face this together.

222
00:20:59.594 --> 00:21:04.297
You. Johnny Cage.
are a part of this now.

223
00:21:13.074 --> 00:21:14.307
Fuck that.

224
00:21:14.441 --> 00:21:15.777
Johnny.
even if you walk away.

225
00:21:15.910 --> 00:21:17.545
the Elder Gods
can still summon you to fight.

226
00:21:17.678 --> 00:21:18.646
Not if they can't find me.

227
00:21:18.780 --> 00:21:20.413
So what are you gonna do. huh?

228
00:21:20.548 --> 00:21:21.883
You just going to go hide?

229
00:21:22.016 --> 00:21:24.085
No. first I'm gonna drink
every beer on the planet.

230
00:21:24.218 --> 00:21:25.586
then I'm going to hide.

231
00:21:25.720 --> 00:21:27.188
Because this shit's
got nothing to do with me.

232
00:21:27.320 --> 00:21:29.157
I'm not some great warrior.

233
00:21:29.289 --> 00:21:30.591
I'm not some champion.

234
00:21:30.725 --> 00:21:33.027
Okay? I'm an actor.

235
00:21:33.161 --> 00:21:34.394
Hmm.

236
00:21:35.263 --> 00:21:36.531
And before that.
you were the guy

237
00:21:36.664 --> 00:21:39.033
with five black belts
and a world title.

238
00:21:40.868 --> 00:21:44.639
Yeah. I saw
some of those old fights.

239
00:21:44.772 --> 00:21:47.842
Man. you could have been
one of the best.

240
00:21:47.975 --> 00:21:50.745
But I wasn't.
And that was a long time ago.

241
00:21:50.878 --> 00:21:54.515
That guy you want
is dead and buried.

242
00:21:54.649 --> 00:21:56.984
Or maybe he's still in there
trying to get out.

243
00:22:17.370 --> 00:22:18.573
Hey. listen...

244
00:22:20.608 --> 00:22:22.777
I'm like 90% sure
I had an aneurysm

245
00:22:22.910 --> 00:22:25.513
and this is some kind of
fucked up coma dream.

246
00:22:27.181 --> 00:22:29.517
but on the off chance
this shit is real.

247
00:22:30.952 --> 00:22:33.120
best of luck with the whole
saving the world thing.

248
00:22:48.368 --> 00:22:51.606
You should know
that when you died.

249
00:22:51.739 --> 00:22:56.443
it was not your so-called
friends who brought you back.

250
00:22:57.410 --> 00:22:59.580
It was not Lord Raiden.

251
00:23:00.348 --> 00:23:02.717
the Great Pretender.

252
00:23:04.218 --> 00:23:06.486
It was Shao Kahn.

253
00:23:07.555 --> 00:23:10.057
Rise now.

254
00:23:10.191 --> 00:23:13.628
as a champion of Outworld.

255
00:23:20.500 --> 00:23:24.071
Sire.
we retrieved the package.

256
00:23:26.173 --> 00:23:27.708
Quan Chi!

257
00:23:27.842 --> 00:23:30.443
I am told you sent your
followers to Earthrealm.

258
00:23:30.578 --> 00:23:31.879
What were they doing there?

259
00:23:32.013 --> 00:23:35.415
Simply retrieving
some lost property. my lady.

260
00:23:35.549 --> 00:23:37.652
By order of your father.

261
00:23:40.087 --> 00:23:41.454
What is that?

262
00:23:45.626 --> 00:23:47.595
I believe it's called...

263
00:23:48.428 --> 00:23:49.797
a "Kano."

264
00:23:54.568 --> 00:23:56.604
One Sling Dog. please.

265
00:24:02.176 --> 00:24:04.278
You're Johnny Cage.

266
00:24:04.412 --> 00:24:05.947
That's what the tab says.

267
00:24:06.080 --> 00:24:07.682
Holy shit.

268
00:24:07.815 --> 00:24:11.919
I freaking loved <i>Citizen Cage</i>
when I was a kid.

269
00:24:13.621 --> 00:24:15.222
Thanks. man. I appreciate it.

270
00:24:17.024 --> 00:24:19.694
Dude. you know
what they should do?

271
00:24:19.827 --> 00:24:22.462
They should
do another <i>Citizen Cage.</i>

272
00:24:22.596 --> 00:24:24.332
Like a reboot.

273
00:24:24.464 --> 00:24:26.867
Come on. man.
Give me a break.

274
00:24:27.001 --> 00:24:29.103
-Nobody wants that.
-What?

275
00:24:29.236 --> 00:24:30.771
You think the world
is crying out

276
00:24:30.905 --> 00:24:34.642
for a Johnny Cage comeback?
Huh?

277
00:24:34.775 --> 00:24:37.111
No. They want gritty.
they want grounded.

278
00:24:37.244 --> 00:24:38.646
they want Keanu Reeves

279
00:24:38.779 --> 00:24:40.480
murdering a thousand
fucking dudes with a pencil.

280
00:24:40.614 --> 00:24:42.583
That's what people wanna see.

281
00:24:44.318 --> 00:24:48.488
Not some dinosaur
doing a bunch of karate poses.

282
00:24:49.489 --> 00:24:51.525
That shit went out
in the '90's.

283
00:24:55.363 --> 00:24:57.098
I thought it was pretty cool.

284
00:25:42.376 --> 00:25:44.678
Where's my fucking eye?

285
00:25:48.249 --> 00:25:49.316
Blondie.

286
00:25:50.651 --> 00:25:52.486
The tournament
has begun.

287
00:25:52.620 --> 00:25:54.688
Today you fight
for Earthrealm.

288
00:25:54.822 --> 00:25:57.224
For the lives of everyone
you have ever known.

289
00:25:57.358 --> 00:26:00.795
If you fail.
the Earth fails with you.

290
00:26:00.928 --> 00:26:04.565
Two of our champions will
be chosen to compete today.

291
00:26:04.698 --> 00:26:05.833
The winners will advance

292
00:26:05.966 --> 00:26:07.835
to the next stage
of the tournament.

293
00:26:07.968 --> 00:26:11.005
The losers will be eliminated.

294
00:26:11.138 --> 00:26:11.872
To the death.

295
00:26:12.006 --> 00:26:13.941
That is up to the winner.

296
00:26:14.842 --> 00:26:16.410
Maybe don't lose.

297
00:26:22.083 --> 00:26:23.884
Well. looks like
it's my lucky day.

298
00:26:24.018 --> 00:26:26.353
Blade. you got this.

299
00:26:32.193 --> 00:26:34.195
I thought you said
two of us were fighting.

300
00:26:38.866 --> 00:26:42.670
<i>It's Johnny Cage</i>
<i>with a brutal hit. He's down.</i>

301
00:26:42.803 --> 00:26:44.305
<i>It's official.</i>

302
00:26:44.438 --> 00:26:47.074
<i>Johnny Cage just became</i>
<i>the youngest minor</i>

303
00:26:47.208 --> 00:26:48.809
<i>to ever win this tournament.</i>

304
00:26:48.943 --> 00:26:51.779
<i>This young man</i>
<i>is destined for greatness.</i>

305
00:26:55.149 --> 00:26:57.918
You seem
a little down. Johnny.

306
00:26:58.052 --> 00:27:00.154
You're normally
a little more animated.

307
00:27:06.760 --> 00:27:08.362
<i>Uno mas.</i> thanks. Ed.

308
00:27:28.482 --> 00:27:30.651
Oh. shit.

309
00:27:35.456 --> 00:27:36.724
I don't know
what you're on about.

310
00:27:36.857 --> 00:27:38.292
The amulet of what now?

311
00:27:38.425 --> 00:27:40.060
Shinnok. Pay attention!

312
00:27:40.194 --> 00:27:41.862
Don't look at me
with that tone of voice.

313
00:27:41.996 --> 00:27:43.364
you big bleached dildo.

314
00:27:43.497 --> 00:27:45.634
I've just been dead.
And my fucking eye's AWOL.

315
00:27:45.766 --> 00:27:49.336
Stop your incessant whinging.
We can build you another.

316
00:27:49.470 --> 00:27:51.272
Why is he not a Revenant
like the rest of them?

317
00:27:51.405 --> 00:27:53.974
He was not worth
the time or the effort.

318
00:27:54.108 --> 00:27:56.744
This one barely has a soul
left to corrupt.

319
00:27:56.877 --> 00:27:58.979
Ha! You hear that?
A fucking loophole.

320
00:27:59.113 --> 00:28:00.549
Go. you good thing.

321
00:28:00.681 --> 00:28:03.817
Where is the amulet you took
from Raiden's temple?

322
00:28:03.951 --> 00:28:05.286
I don't know.
probably in my pocket

323
00:28:05.419 --> 00:28:07.087
where I keep
all the shit I steal.

324
00:28:08.657 --> 00:28:10.391
Oh. right-oh.

325
00:28:12.527 --> 00:28:16.631
Here we go. How about...

326
00:28:16.764 --> 00:28:19.534
Nah. different temple.
Well. hold on.

327
00:28:19.668 --> 00:28:21.035
This could be...

328
00:28:21.168 --> 00:28:23.237
Yeah.
Should call her.

329
00:28:24.004 --> 00:28:27.208
Ah! Here we are. Yahtzee.

330
00:28:27.741 --> 00:28:28.677
Oi!

331
00:28:28.809 --> 00:28:29.843
We could have left him dead.

332
00:28:29.977 --> 00:28:31.745
Hey! First off. fuck off.

333
00:28:31.879 --> 00:28:33.881
And you.
where are you going with that?

334
00:28:34.882 --> 00:28:36.483
I will take it to my father.

335
00:28:37.851 --> 00:28:39.086
Unfortunately. Princess.

336
00:28:39.220 --> 00:28:41.722
it appears
you are needed elsewhere.

337
00:28:43.958 --> 00:28:45.627
Oi. you creepy fucking mime.

338
00:28:45.759 --> 00:28:47.895
I stole that fair and square.

339
00:28:48.896 --> 00:28:50.197
Good luck.

340
00:29:11.018 --> 00:29:13.688
Each flame
represents a fighter.

341
00:29:13.854 --> 00:29:15.022
The tournament ends
when one side

342
00:29:15.155 --> 00:29:16.957
has no champions left.

343
00:29:17.825 --> 00:29:19.360
Hey. How's it going. babe?

344
00:29:21.529 --> 00:29:24.699
Listen. I'm warning you.

345
00:29:24.832 --> 00:29:27.868
I got a Saturn Award for
best fight in a feature film.

346
00:29:28.002 --> 00:29:29.571
so don't mess with me.

347
00:29:33.575 --> 00:29:35.577
Whoa! Whoa. Easy. all right.

348
00:29:35.710 --> 00:29:38.112
Let's just take a timeout here
and talk about it.

349
00:29:38.245 --> 00:29:41.248
Okay? I really don't feel
comfortable hitting a girl.

350
00:29:42.850 --> 00:29:45.219
Don't worry. you won't.

351
00:29:56.463 --> 00:29:58.499
Whoa! Come on. Easy.
Let's just talk about this.

352
00:30:21.422 --> 00:30:22.856
Why are you so fucking mean?

353
00:32:15.537 --> 00:32:16.970
Finish him!

354
00:32:31.084 --> 00:32:32.419
Hmm.

355
00:32:56.376 --> 00:32:59.079
It appears your side
is already down a man.

356
00:33:00.047 --> 00:33:01.315
Tragic.

357
00:33:04.218 --> 00:33:05.452
And who are you?

358
00:33:05.587 --> 00:33:08.255
Sindel. High Queen of Edenia.

359
00:33:08.388 --> 00:33:10.959
Consort to the great
Shao Kahn.

360
00:33:11.091 --> 00:33:12.993
They send their queen
to fight?

361
00:33:13.126 --> 00:33:16.497
No. We send our best to fight.

362
00:33:16.898 --> 00:33:18.332
Oh.

363
00:33:18.465 --> 00:33:20.501
No offense. babe. but you look
really fucking dead.

364
00:33:20.635 --> 00:33:22.971
I was freed
from my mortal bonds.

365
00:33:23.103 --> 00:33:24.238
Shao Kahn showed me

366
00:33:24.371 --> 00:33:25.940
the pleasures
of a life eternal.

367
00:33:30.512 --> 00:33:32.580
Perhaps I'll do the same
for you.

368
00:33:42.389 --> 00:33:44.692
What a pretty trick.

369
00:33:44.826 --> 00:33:47.060
Would you like to see mine?

370
00:33:47.194 --> 00:33:49.096
No. actually I'm good.

371
00:34:12.052 --> 00:34:14.756
Fuck you!
You stupid bitch!

372
00:35:21.388 --> 00:35:23.524
It appears
our sides are now even.

373
00:35:28.596 --> 00:35:30.464
What'd I miss?

374
00:35:30.598 --> 00:35:33.133
Fuck yeah! Look who's back.

375
00:35:34.602 --> 00:35:36.804
Well? How bad was it?

376
00:35:36.938 --> 00:35:40.307
Zombie queen.
Pit of spikes. Yeah.

377
00:35:40.440 --> 00:35:42.110
-So pretty goddamn bad.
-Ow.

378
00:35:43.878 --> 00:35:45.345
-You okay?
-Yeah.

379
00:35:49.817 --> 00:35:50.885
What happened?

380
00:35:51.019 --> 00:35:53.353
You were eliminated
from the tournament.

381
00:35:54.221 --> 00:35:55.690
You lost.

382
00:35:55.823 --> 00:35:58.526
You are lucky. she was
charitable and let you live.

383
00:36:06.166 --> 00:36:07.702
Oi! Pennywise.

384
00:36:07.835 --> 00:36:10.104
I've been looking all over
this shithole for you.

385
00:36:10.237 --> 00:36:11.639
You promised me a new eye.

386
00:36:11.773 --> 00:36:13.775
And it better be one
that shoots lasers.

387
00:36:13.908 --> 00:36:16.811
- I have other priorities.
- Like fucking what?

388
00:36:16.944 --> 00:36:18.478
If it's putting on
more eyeliner.

389
00:36:18.613 --> 00:36:20.114
trust me. you're good.

390
00:36:20.247 --> 00:36:21.549
All right? Come on. mate.

391
00:36:21.683 --> 00:36:23.851
I am bumping into shit
left. right. and center.

392
00:36:23.985 --> 00:36:25.887
I mean. my peripheral vision
is fucked.

393
00:36:26.020 --> 00:36:27.522
Proper fucked. mate.

394
00:36:27.655 --> 00:36:29.724
So come on.
Chop-chop. Let's get to it.

395
00:36:31.358 --> 00:36:32.794
Well. you don't have
to do it right now.

396
00:36:32.927 --> 00:36:35.630
I mean. you need to.
you know. take a measurement.

397
00:36:35.763 --> 00:36:39.366
Check the color or wash
your grubby little hands.

398
00:36:42.202 --> 00:36:43.638
All right. let's have a look.

399
00:36:43.771 --> 00:36:46.708
Don't fucking roll it on
the fucking ground. you grub!

400
00:36:48.076 --> 00:36:50.243
Oi. the amulet.

401
00:36:50.377 --> 00:36:52.780
I want that back.
And don't fucking roll it.

402
00:36:52.914 --> 00:36:55.650
You got your eye.
Now leave me alone.

403
00:36:55.783 --> 00:36:58.351
The amulet
does not belong to you.

404
00:36:58.485 --> 00:37:00.287
Its powers are well beyond

405
00:37:00.420 --> 00:37:02.523
your meager understanding.

406
00:37:02.657 --> 00:37:03.891
Idiot.

407
00:37:04.025 --> 00:37:05.760
All right. Let's take
this baby for a test drive.

408
00:37:06.661 --> 00:37:09.463
All right.

409
00:37:09.597 --> 00:37:14.602
One. two. three.
Oh! Fuck! Snug.

410
00:37:17.471 --> 00:37:18.973
Wow.

411
00:37:19.107 --> 00:37:21.509
Holy shit. is that HD?
That's pretty good.

412
00:37:21.642 --> 00:37:24.377
How many eyes you made?
Can you do me other one?

413
00:37:37.457 --> 00:37:39.560
You seem troubled. Mr. Cage.

414
00:37:41.195 --> 00:37:43.296
Yeah. Well. 'cause of me

415
00:37:43.430 --> 00:37:46.067
Earth's odds
just got 20% worse.

416
00:37:46.200 --> 00:37:48.503
I had a chance to actually
do something worth a damn

417
00:37:48.636 --> 00:37:50.071
and I screwed it all up.

418
00:37:50.204 --> 00:37:54.675
So. yeah. I'd say "troubled"
just about sums it up.

419
00:38:02.583 --> 00:38:05.820
What are those? Pills?

420
00:38:06.286 --> 00:38:07.989
Huh?

421
00:38:08.122 --> 00:38:09.657
Are they magic fighting pills?

422
00:38:10.725 --> 00:38:12.860
Is that how
you get your powers?

423
00:38:22.170 --> 00:38:23.403
Bird seed.

424
00:38:24.739 --> 00:38:29.043
Oh. Yeah. yeah. yeah.
Bird seed. Yeah.

425
00:38:29.177 --> 00:38:32.613
Well. I thought you were gonna
give me some kind of lecture.

426
00:38:32.747 --> 00:38:36.651
but. yeah. chores are good.

427
00:38:39.120 --> 00:38:40.988
You don't need a lecture.

428
00:38:41.122 --> 00:38:42.422
You need perspective.

429
00:38:42.557 --> 00:38:44.926
Perspective. huh?

430
00:38:45.059 --> 00:38:47.360
There are eight billion people
on this planet

431
00:38:47.494 --> 00:38:49.530
and yet the gods chose you.

432
00:38:49.664 --> 00:38:51.599
Perhaps they saw
your true potential

433
00:38:51.732 --> 00:38:54.202
as a champion of Earthrealm.

434
00:38:54.334 --> 00:38:55.903
Maybe they made a mistake.

435
00:38:56.037 --> 00:38:57.205
Maybe.

436
00:38:57.337 --> 00:39:00.608
If I see the Elder Gods.
I'll be sure to tell them.

437
00:39:05.079 --> 00:39:08.649
Well. I'm glad
you find this all so amusing.

438
00:39:08.783 --> 00:39:12.587
Hey. great pep talk.
by the way. Just nailed it.

439
00:39:58.299 --> 00:39:59.499
Ouch.

440
00:40:00.534 --> 00:40:02.536
You have done this before?

441
00:40:03.337 --> 00:40:04.739
I've seen it done.

442
00:40:06.540 --> 00:40:07.708
All right.

443
00:40:12.880 --> 00:40:16.584
It's okay. The Princess Kitana
has been my eyes and ears

444
00:40:16.717 --> 00:40:18.819
inside the palace
for many years now.

445
00:40:20.154 --> 00:40:22.323
We know the risk you took
coming here.

446
00:40:22.489 --> 00:40:23.724
Thank you. Kitana.

447
00:40:23.858 --> 00:40:26.060
Wait. are you telling me
I got my ass kicked

448
00:40:26.193 --> 00:40:27.460
by one of the good guys?

449
00:40:27.595 --> 00:40:30.965
I had to make it look real.
He was watching.

450
00:40:31.098 --> 00:40:33.301
They found
the Amulet of Shinnok.

451
00:40:33.433 --> 00:40:34.568
It was in the possession

452
00:40:34.702 --> 00:40:36.404
of a dead sellsword
named Kano.

453
00:40:36.537 --> 00:40:37.972
Son of a bitch.

454
00:40:38.105 --> 00:40:39.974
If the Emperor finds a way
to charge the amulet.

455
00:40:40.107 --> 00:40:41.676
he would be unstoppable.

456
00:40:41.809 --> 00:40:43.344
It would be
like fighting a god.

457
00:40:43.476 --> 00:40:46.547
Yeah. well. let's not do that.

458
00:40:46.681 --> 00:40:49.482
My friend
is in the tournament.

459
00:40:49.617 --> 00:40:52.053
Jade was raised
under Shao Kahn's army.

460
00:40:52.186 --> 00:40:56.456
Do what you must.
but do not make her suffer.

461
00:41:08.468 --> 00:41:10.604
You went to another realm?

462
00:41:12.740 --> 00:41:13.941
You followed me?

463
00:41:14.075 --> 00:41:16.277
I am trying to keep you alive.

464
00:41:16.410 --> 00:41:17.712
By spying on your friend.

465
00:41:17.845 --> 00:41:20.147
By keeping my friend
from making a mistake.

466
00:41:20.281 --> 00:41:23.751
You are conspiring
with Lord Raiden. The enemy.

467
00:41:23.884 --> 00:41:26.854
I swore an oath. Kitana.

468
00:41:26.988 --> 00:41:30.791
To serve as Shao Kahn's sword.

469
00:41:38.032 --> 00:41:39.767
The second round
of the tournament

470
00:41:39.900 --> 00:41:42.370
will consist of three matches.

471
00:41:42.502 --> 00:41:45.573
Jax. Cole. Liu Kang.

472
00:42:02.757 --> 00:42:04.258
Kung Lao.

473
00:42:05.393 --> 00:42:07.061
I have been given new life.

474
00:42:08.362 --> 00:42:09.830
My son?

475
00:42:18.773 --> 00:42:22.410
Look at that.
Still part of this tournament.

476
00:42:22.543 --> 00:42:24.045
But that's not why I'm here.

477
00:42:33.120 --> 00:42:34.989
No!

478
00:42:35.122 --> 00:42:36.223
No!

479
00:42:47.668 --> 00:42:49.136
Attack now!

480
00:43:27.675 --> 00:43:33.347
Imagine what one
could do with such power.

481
00:43:33.481 --> 00:43:38.285
Careful. Sorcerer.
that doesn't belong to you.

482
00:43:45.693 --> 00:43:48.662
The amulet must be bound
to a mortal soul.

483
00:43:48.796 --> 00:43:50.631
Once it has imprinted
on to you.

484
00:43:50.764 --> 00:43:53.067
Raiden's power will be yours.

485
00:43:53.200 --> 00:43:55.669
The amulet
will give you immortality.

486
00:44:59.568 --> 00:45:03.237
Well. this is fucking ominous.

487
00:45:09.910 --> 00:45:11.680
I'm guessing you're Jade.

488
00:45:11.812 --> 00:45:13.714
Let's get this over with.

489
00:45:19.286 --> 00:45:22.022
I am told you carry
the blood of Scorpion.

490
00:45:26.060 --> 00:45:28.195
I look forward to spilling it.

491
00:45:42.476 --> 00:45:44.812
You know you're fighting
on the wrong side. right?

492
00:45:55.322 --> 00:45:57.491
What the fuck
do you have under there?

493
00:45:58.759 --> 00:46:00.995
Shit.

494
00:46:20.848 --> 00:46:22.016
Well. hello there.

495
00:46:30.257 --> 00:46:33.060
I hope
your ancestors are watching.

496
00:47:04.526 --> 00:47:07.961
For what it is worth.
I take no joy in this.

497
00:47:10.532 --> 00:47:12.833
Then you're really going
to hate this shit.

498
00:47:18.072 --> 00:47:19.607
This is for my family.

499
00:47:20.809 --> 00:47:22.811
For my friends.

500
00:47:22.943 --> 00:47:25.479
For every moment
that brought me here.

501
00:47:25.613 --> 00:47:29.316
This is for Earth.
you son of a bitch.

502
00:48:17.766 --> 00:48:18.932
What?

503
00:48:43.424 --> 00:48:45.660
Give my regards to the dead.

504
00:48:54.501 --> 00:48:57.371
Go on. do it.

505
00:49:20.829 --> 00:49:22.362
Why?

506
00:49:22.496 --> 00:49:24.632
Your friend spared
one of our guys.

507
00:49:25.834 --> 00:49:26.967
Now we're even.

